descriptionHtml:
[b][i] [size=14]Introduction[/size][/i][/b]

I can't speak English well.

This is a conversion of "Tonas Mods Store" in Oblivion mode.
Original author is Tona.
Original link : [url=http://oblivion.nexusmods.com/mods/29090]http://oblivion.nexusmods.com/mods/29090[/url]

This Mod has Gomdori Armor.

[b][i] [size=14]Caution[/size][/i][/b]

[color=red]My skyrim version is 1.8.151. I made a esp file with newest CK.[/color]
[color=red]If your version is lower than 1.8, you have nothing in craft list, console(help command).[/color]
[color=red]You must update new version.[/color]

[b][i] [size=14]Description[/size][/i][/b]

[img]http://i.imgur.com/0le8Z.jpg[/img]

[img]http://i.imgur.com/BFJah.jpg[/img]

[img]http://i.imgur.com/28vnX.jpg[/img]

[img]http://i.imgur.com/Qswdx.jpg[/img]

Here are armor, glove, boots & helmet (brown & white).

These are craftable & smithing at Daedric, DragonScale that made forge menu.

[color=yellow]You can find that begin with "Gomdori".[/color]

[b][i] [size=14]Compatibility[/size][/i][/b]

It can wear with every body type(cbbe, unp, tbbp etc).
It is only for female.
